ramid_Hill_-_NARA_-_7722147.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ac/Sheyenne_River_Valley_Scenic_Byway_-_Reading_about_Pyramid_Hill_-_NARA_-_7722166.jpg/1280px-Sheyenne_River_Valley_Scenic_Byway_-_Reading_about_Pyramid_Hill_-_NARA_-_7722166.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ac/Sheyenne_River_Valley_Scenic_Byway_-_Reading_about_Pyramid_Hill_-_NARA_-_7722166.jpg","cap":"Sheyenne River Valley Scenic Byway Reading about Pyramid Hill","desc":"Two travelers find the legends of Pyramid Hill fascinating. Location: Fort Ransom, North Dakota (46.519° N 97.940° W) Status: Public domain. Photo by S. Clyde","credit":"S. Clyde · Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Sheyenne_River_Valley_Scenic_Byway_-_Reading_about_Pyramid_Hill_-_NARA_-_7722166.jpg"}]}